{"tid":1389201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[淺見] 葵涌一役給我們的三大啟示","createTime":"2019-07-31T00:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:45:59.000Z","uid":140213,"like":313,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"1524e82cdf6c0119c084cf10faa135aa1caf1202","tid":1389201,"uid":140213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"葵涌警署嘅突襲令狗措手不及<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實勇武嘅兄弟們應該諗諗依個方向<br />\n<br />\n1. 警力不足<br />\n勇武嘅兄弟其實已經有唔錯嘅裝備，但係，奈何狗隻速龍同未來<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">水炮車</span></span>，只會令更多兄弟送頭。突擊先能夠將實力拉近，建議勇武摒棄&ldquo;今次唔衝幾時衝&rdquo;嘅心態，利用依d機會打游擊，只要有十幾個勇武巴打，已經夠收佢地皮。例子如光頭佬被打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 抗爭地方化<br />\n同以往嘅包警總唔同，今次組織嘅都係同區市民，咁樣嘅抗爭係更能夠be <span style=\"color: red;\">be water</span> ，令狗由不同環頭調配，疲於奔命，同時，市民熟悉區內道路，有利逃走。<br />\n<br />\n3. 確立目標<br />\n上環之役比人講嘅地方係目標唔清晰，相反，今次大家都明係要支援義士，同埋打狗，依一點令更多和理非可以落場支持，記住，多人我地就唔撚洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，勇武和理非可以互相補位，減少被捕風險。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0231d8b58e041e86da85377cddb318659fadf7ad","tid":1389201,"uid":140213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d06b8e437c4ef32a686042d44f702ecb1e394","tid":1389201,"uid":140213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20bfacf5c3fa4cc800d9afd6b18c863e65bb17d","tid":1389201,"uid":140213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:23:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8376106acc649f8df0043a32a5b1ccf6404726dd","tid":1389201,"uid":140213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:23:43.000Z","msg":"<im